```r
sinspuBrayPCoAMetaVir %>%
  dplyr::select(index,most.ab,virus.ct,ct) %>%
  inner_join(.,sinspuPCoAMeta) -> sinspuPCoAMeta

sinspuPCoAMeta %>%
  group_by(most.ab) %>%
  summarise(ab.Dim1 = mean(Dim1),
            ab.Dim2 = mean(Dim2)) -> mostabCentroid

ggplot(sinspuPCoAMeta,
       aes(x = Dim1,
           y = Dim2,
           color = most.ab)) +
  geom_point(size = 2,
             alpha = 0.5) +
  scale_color_manual(name = \Most abundant genera\"
